      <p class="pdesc">Autonomous biometric decision-support system integrating Bangle.js smartwatch PPG/HRV data and Meta Ray-Ban smart glasses for real-time decision-risk prediction. On-device XGBoost ML with 36 biosignal features trained on 70,000+ multimodal instances.</p>
